SUMMARY:Women's Connection Study | Monday Evenings
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we study the Gospel of Mark. Mark recounts the life\, teachings\, miracles\, death and resurrection of Jesus\, urging its readers to respond in faith and follow Him in discipleship and sacrifice. \nMonday Evenings | MP3 at MBCS \n6:45pm – 8:15pm \nSeptember 22\, 2025 – May 11\, 2026 \nWINTER BREAK: December 15 – January 19 \nClick Here to Register Now \n 
URL:https://ggwo.org/ggwo-event/womens-connection-study-monday-evenings/2026-03-16/
CATEGORIES:Women
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ggwo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Mark-1920-x-1080-px.jpg
END:VEVENT
