SUMMARY:Active Assailant Response Training
DESCRIPTION:March 25 | 9A-12P | Classroom 2 / MBCS \nACTIVE ASSAILANT TRAINING \nBe prepared. Be informed. Be empowered. \nJoin our Active Assailant Response Training and gain life-saving strategies\nfor responding to an active threat. In this interactive 2.5-hour course\,\nparticipants learn practical\, real-world techniques to strengthen personal\,\nworkplace\, and campus safety.  \nSpace is limited—please register early to secure your spot. This event is free of charge.  \nClick Here to Register Now
URL:https://ggwo.org/ggwo-event/active-assailant-response-training/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://ggwo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Screenshot-2026-03-03-at-09.42.08.png
END:VEVENT
