SUMMARY:Married Couples' Night Out
DESCRIPTION:Married Couples Night Out\nFriday\, April 10\, 2026 | 6-9P | Blackwall Hitch Baltimore Restaurant \nSlow down. Share a meal. Connect with other couples. \nWe’ve reserved a room at a local restaurant for a relaxed\, low-key evening designed simply to be together — a chance to connect with other couples\, be encouraged\, and focus on what matters most. \nRegistration required and seating is limited — registration closes April 2nd\nCost: $120 per couple \nCome hang out — we’d love to see you there! \n\nRegister and Food Menu
URL:https://ggwo.org/ggwo-event/married-couples-night-out/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ggwo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/medium_image-1772484287729.jpeg
